<paragraph id="2301F94A658ACD263433AA0B327A6B2E" pageId="2" pageNumber="41">Relation to the host plant.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1122A7E6D7186E62C9F69A8ABD03C7AA" pageId="2" pageNumber="41">The mites inhabit the under surface of leaves as vagrants without showing symptoms of damage to the host plant.</paragraph>
